metadata.name: "Slava Ukraini - Heroines of Valor" by JLP_NFT
metadata.description: "Slava Ukraini - Heroines of Valor" is a captivating oil painting NFT that pays tribute to the indomitable spirit and bravery of Ukrainian women who have tirelessly fought and assisted in the uneven battles for their homeland. The digital artwork is a harmonious blend of traditional oil painting techniques and cutting-edge  technology, bringing together the past and present to commemorate the strength and resilience of these heroic women.
